      "notes": [
        {
          "category": "summary",
          "text": "The affected product is vulnerable due to a component within the affected application that regularly calls a helper binary with SYSTEM privileges while the call path is not quoted, potentially allowing an attacker to execute commands with elevated privileges.CVE-2020-7580 has been assigned to this vulnerability. A CVSS v3 base score of 6.7 has been calculated; the CVSS vector string is (AV:L/AC:L/PR:H/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:H).",
